2f9f9581dc965fd87d787ae2adb332edf21445c93e39\">\n            <summary>Bump updatecli version</summary>\n            <p>1 file(s) updated with &#34;v0.112.0&#34;:&#xA;&#xA;* updatecli/install/.default-updatecli-version&#xA;</p>\n            <details>\n                <summary>v0.112.0</summary>\n                <pre>&gt; [!WARNING]&#xD;&#xA;&gt; In the previous version (v0.111.0,  a regression was introduced in the GitLab action, where Updatecli automatically enables auto merge request.&#xD;&#xA;&gt; This wasn&#39;t intend and is now reverted to the previous behavior. By default, Updatecli doesn&#39;t auto merge GitLab merge request&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## Changes&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## 🚀 Features&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- refactor: gitlab client-go migration @chrxmvtik (#7157)&#xD;&#xA;- feat: add --pipeline-ids param @olblak (#7121)&#xD;&#xA;- feat: add pnpm npm autodiscovery @loispostula (#7035)&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## 🐛 Bug Fixes&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- fix(autodiscovery/dockerfile): add regex field support for versionfilter @loispostula (#7140)&#xD;&#xA;- feat: add option to disable automerge in Gitlab @d0mitoridesu (#7036)&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## 🧰 Maintenance&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module gitlab.com/gitlab-org/api/client-go to v1.8.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7176)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module golang.org/x/oauth2 to v0.34.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7175)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module github.com/spf13/cobra to v1.10.2 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7186)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module golang.org/x/mod to v0.31.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7177)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module github.com/fluxcd/helm-controller/api to v1.4.5 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7187)&#xD;&#xA;- deps: bump golangci-lint to v2.7.2 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7174)&#xD;&#xA;- chore(dockerfile): upgrade node version @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7122)&#xD;&#xA;- deps: Bump Golang version to 1.25.5 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7158)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/config to v1.32.4 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7111)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2 to v1.40.1 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7079)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(updatecli/policies): bump all policies @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7066)&#xD;&#xA;- deps(go): bump module github.com/drone/go-scm to v1.41.0 @[updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot) (#7054)&#xD;&#xA;- fix: redact version v0.999.0 @olblak (#7019)&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## 📝 Documentation&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- docs: fix how to verify release assets @suzuki-shunsuke (#7033)&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## Contributors&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;@chrxmvtik, @d0mitoridesu, @loispostula, @olblak, @suzuki-shunsuke, @updateclibot[bot] and [updateclibot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/updateclibot)&#xD;&#xA;</pre>\n            </details>\n        </details>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/elastic/oblt-actions/actions/runs/20390159743\">GitHub Action workflow link</a>\n    </action>\n</Actions>\n\n---\n\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td width=\"77\">\n      <img src=\"https://www.updatecli.io/images/updatecli.png\" alt=\"Updatecli logo\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" />\n    </td>\n    <td>\n      <p>\n        Created automatically by <a href=\"https://www.updatecli.io/\">Updatecli</a>\n      </p>\n      <details><summary>Options:</summary>\n        <br />\n        <p>Most of Updatecli configuration is done via <a href=\"https://www.updatecli.io/docs/prologue/quick-start/\">its manifest(s)</a>.</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li>If you close this pull request, Updatecli will automatically reopen it, the next time it runs.</li>\n          <li>If you clos